* Carnage snarled at Tritan, it was WAY to late now! She was sure that his color had given them away anyway, it had only been a matter of time!
She sighed and then turned her attention back to Teltoli, what in the....*

" Slag!"

* There was a shoot out, and it seemed that Teltoli and Dracona were right in the middle of it!
Carnage growled as she began to creep back around to her original position where she had been drinking before, once there she looked over at Teltoli and opened her com-link to her...*

" Hay! Guess who? Never mind, no time for jokes. Anyway, it seems to me that those goons are all Alliance members. Or at least one of them. It'll be better if we leave the scene instead of sticking around to fight.
But just in case these bots want to rumble I'll cover us. Kay?"

* With that said she deactivated her communicater and then stood back a bit, with her eyes on the fighting bots...*

" Carnage...TRANSFORM!!!"

* With the sound of turning gears she transformed and stepped out of the surrounding brush, with a snarl she reached behind herself and came back with a phaser.
Carnage looked across the lake at Teltoli, she didn't want her friend to get hurt but if she was going to stay then she was going to stay and fight too!
She gestured with her gun for Teltoli to beat it but she wasn't sure if the Fuzor saw it, but she would find out soon enough.
Carnage then turned her head back towards the fighting bots, if they were any danger to her Maximal friend or Teltoli's new friend (Plintissa)then they would have to deal with her first!*
